title: Photos: Varun Dhawan & His Girlfriend At Shahid Kapoor’s Birthday Party
text:
Rashmi Daryanani Feb . 20 . 2017 
Varun Dhawan and girlfriend Natasha Dalal were spotted recently when they spent Valentine’s Day together , and the two were photographed again this weekend at Shahid Kapoor ‘s early birthday party. Photos: Varun Dhawan and Natasha Dalal Varun Dhawan and Natasha Dalal Varun Dhawan and Natasha Dalal Varun Dhawan and Natasha Dalal Varun Dhawan and Natasha Dalal ‹ › ‹ › 
Several other A-Listers, like Deepika Padukone, Katrina Kaif, Ranveer Singh, Sonakshi Sinha, Sidharth Malhotra and Alia Bhatt also attended Shahid’s party. 0
